Class ParserAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gate.util.AbstractFeatureBearer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    gate.creole.ANNIEConstants, gate.Executable, gate.LanguageAnalyser, gate.ProcessingResource, gate.Resource, gate.util.FeatureBearer, gate.util.NameBearer, Serializable

    public class ParserAnnotator
extends gate.creole.AbstractLanguageAnalyser
    Wrapper for the RASP Parser, which generates dependencies between Tokens but also a syntactic analysis. This annotator requires a preliminary analysis with the POS tagger and morphological analyser
